  "title": "Forklift Operator (Tuas/ Jurong Island)",
  "description": "<p>Our esteemed client in the <strong>Logistics industry</strong> is seeking a <strong>Forklift Driver </strong>to join their dynamic team:</p><ul><li><strong>Employment Type: </strong>Permanent</li><li><strong>Position:</strong> Forklift Driver</li><li><strong>Location:</strong> Jurong Island (Transport provided in the west area)/ Tuas</li><li><strong>Working Hours:</strong> 5.5 days (Mon to Fri, 8AM to 5PM, Sat 8AM to 12PM)</li><li><strong>Salary Package:</strong> Up to $2,900 + Island Allowance + AWS + Bonus</li></ul><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Operate forklift safely and efficiently to support warehouse and production activities.</li><li>Handle Container stuffing and unstuffing</li><li>Perform loading and unloading of goods</li><li>Handle shifting of goods, ensuring proper storage and inventory arrangement.</li><li>Conduct daily checks, upkeep, and basic maintenance of the forklift.</li><li>Other duties as assigned by the Supervisor.</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>At least 1 year of experience in operating forklift.</li><li>Must have a valid forklift license.</li><li>Possess own motorbike would be recommended</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Ready to apply? Here’s how:</strong></p><ul><li>Click the APPLY button, or</li><li>Email your resume (in MS Word or PDF format) to <a href=\"mailto:adelin@intuitrecruitment.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>adelin@intuitrecruitment.com</strong>.</a> Include the job title in your email subject line for prompt processing.</li></ul><p><em><strong>Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</strong></em></p><p><br /></p><p>By submitting your application, you consent to the collection and use of your personal data under Personal Data Protection Act (PDPA).</p><p><br /></p><p>Adelin Chong | EA Personnel Reg No.: R1875641</p><p>Intuit Recruitment Pte Ltd | EA License No.: 25C2793</p>",
